data.description: This lovely home in the heart of Lyman is well maintained and move-in ready! All appliances remain (including refrigerator, washer and dryer!), new flooring has been installed throughout, the tv above the fireplace remains and the blinds are already in place so all buyers need to do is unpack and enjoy this beautiful home. The covered front porch welcomes you to the main entry hall and large Dining Room (which can also be used as a Flex room, Den, Play room, Office or Workout room). Down the hall is a Half Bath, an oversized storage closet and access to the 2 Car Garage. The Kitchen, Breakfast Room and Living Room offer an easy flow with a great open floor plan. The Living Room has a fireplace with gas logs, ceiling fan and a mounted TV above the fireplace that remains. The Kitchen has bar seating at the island, a Breakfast area for an additional table, stainless appliances that all remain (including the refrigerator!) and a large Pantry for plenty of storage. This area leads to the extended patio and private backyard. Upstairs includes the bedroom area which is nicely separated for privacy and the Laundry Room nearby for convenience. The Primary Suite includes an oversized Bedroom with space for an owner's den, a huge walk-in closet and a large primary Bathroom with double vanity, separate shower and garden tub.  The two additional bedrooms are very spacious and also have walk-in closets! There is a large loft area that could be used as a den, office, playroom, movie room or as a 4th Bedroom since it also has a closet. The walk-in Laundry Room is also upstairs to add the convenience of being near the bedrooms. This is a wonderful home that is move-in ready and truly better than new with easy access to I-85, I-26, Spartanburg, Greer and Greenville!
